      "id": "takeaway_text",
      "x": 90,
      "y": 960,
      "width": 1020,
      "height": 40,
      "text": "Pathways = Client + Resource Manager + Plaque (distributed daemons) + Sharded Object Store.\nGang scheduling prevents deadlock. Async dispatch hides latency. Data stays on-device.",
